high_descs: Turn left, turn left at the fridge and walk to the sink.
Pick up the potato to the right of the sink.
Turn to the right and face the microwave.
Place the potato inside the microwave to the left of the white mug, heat the potato, take the potato out of the microwave, and close the door.
Turn left to face the sink.
Put the potato down on the counter to the right of the sink.
anns.task_desc: To heat a potato and put it on the counter next to the sink.

high_descs: Turn to your left then walk forward then turn left head to the counter beside the sink
Pick up the potato on the counter beside the sink
Turn to your right move slightly then face the microwave on your left
Open the microwave put in the potato then take it out, close the microwave
Turn to your left facing the counter beside the sink
Put the potato on the edge of the counter beside the knife
anns.task_desc: Put the heated potato on the counter beside the sink

high_descs: Turn around and move towards the sink
Pick up the dark brown vegetable from the right of the sink
Turn to the microwave to the right
Open the microwave and place the brown vegetable inside, close microwave, start it, open microwave and remove brown vegetable
Place the brown vegetable on the counter just above the knife and below the spatula to the right of the sink
anns.task_desc: Heating up a vegetable and putting it on the counter
